                      Caregiver Handbook - coming soon

   The Older Americans Act Amendments of 2000 established an important new
   program, the National Family Caregiver Support Program (NFCSP). This
   site has been established to assist the aging network to develop
   caregiver support programs.
   __________________________________________________________________

FYI:  The Brookdale Foundation has announced the 2002 Relatives as Parents
Program (RAPP) State Seed Grant Initiative. Contact the Brookdale Foundation,
212-308-7355, for details.  (Courtesy Listing: This is not a federal
government program.)

