   FY 2001 Grants To Support Family Caregivers [PDF version]

   Enrollment of SUA and AAA staff on AoA Caregiver Listserv

   Call for Proposals -  Third International Conference on Family Care -
   to provide a forum for caregiving groups, advocates and policy makers
   from around the globe to exchange ideas on innovative and effective
   ways to empower and assist family caregivers. The conference will be
   held in Washington, DC, on October 12-14, 2002.  The call for proposals
   for the is now available online and the deadline for submissions is
   January 25, 2002.
